results.name: Difference between A053644 (the largest power of 2 less than or equal to n) and its Möbius transform.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..65537
mathematica: With[{s = Array[2^Floor@ Log2@ # &, 95]}, Table[s[[n]] - DivisorSum[n, MoebiusMu[n/#] s[[#]] &], {n, Length@ s}]] (* _Michael De Vlieger_, Mar 13 2018 *)
